Package group10.client.entity

Class PagedEntity<T>

java.lang.Object
group10.client.entity.PagedEntity<T>
public class PagedEntity<T> extends Object
Generic class of Paged Entity for parsing JSON responses from the server Developed according to the Pageable interface of Spring.
Author:
Alperen Caykus, Mustafa Ozan Alpay
